Reynders Says Government Will Act If Needed to Support Dexia

-- B y   J o n e s   H a y d e n
-- 
2011-10-04T07:26:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/reynders-says-government-will-act-if-needed-to-support-dexia.html
Belgian Finance Minister  Didier
Reynders  said the government will act if necessary to support
 Dexia SA. (DEXB)   “If it is needed we will act,” Reynders told reporters
today in Luxembourg. “First of all, we need to read all the
proposals coming from the bank,” he said.  “We will see all the proposals coming from the board
meeting” last night, Reynders said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jones Hayden at 
 jhayden1@bloomberg.net  